your holiday must be paid in full, via a wire transfer, to the tourism council of bhutan account before a tourist visa is issued. visa clearance takes no longer than 72 hours, once full payment has been received. at your point of entry the visa will be stamped in your passport on payment of us$20, two passport photos will also be required. visa extensions can be obtained through you local tour operator at a cost of nu.600 (1 ngultrum = 1 indian rupee) and the tourist will also be subject to the daily tariff for the additional days. visas are 